Package: MixOptim
Type: Package
Title: Mixture optmization algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cassandro Davi Emer
Maintainer: Cassandro Davi Emer <cde@actisys.org>
Description: MixOptim is a simple package to perform mixture optimization based on the 'desirability' package by Max Kuhn.
    It also provides a plot routine using ggplot and patchwork.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: ggplot2, patchwork, desirability
